      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACQUISITIVE ART (6) sound debut in the heavy (10) going with an eye-catching second over 800m at Narromine. Likely improver over the extra trip with the senior rider booked. Can go one better here. EUPHORIC MISS (7) gets in light with the 4kg claimer retaining the ride from a soft draw. Failed to stretch out in the conditions with a tiring fifth over 900m at Coonabarabran. Close to her top for this and sure to be thereabouts. SCATHINGLY (4) has come back much stronger this prep and a win looks imminent. Had genuine excuses from a wide draw with a fading sixth over 1200m at this track. Can stalk the speed here and take holding out. SPELLECAST (5) finds an easier race on the back-up after he surged forward from an outside gate before tiring to run seventh over 1000m at this track. Each-way contender with the claim.",
